ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention concerning Labour Inspection in Industry and Commerce
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the CONVENTION CONCERNING LABOUR INSPECTION IN INDUSTRY AND COMMERCE adopted at Geneva on July 11, 1947 in order to ratify Convention 81 and Protocol 29 and to ensure respect for fundamental principles and rights at work.
